{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "projects",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 02_projects\nCONTEXT — work that **ends**.\n\nOne folder each.\nOverview + tasks + decisions.",
      "x": -20,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "areas",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 03_areas\nCONTEXT — work that **never ends**.\n\nSupport, review, team.\nNo finish line.",
      "x": 360,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "system",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 00_system — STEERING\n\nSits outside the flow and governs all of it.\n\n- `CLAUDE.md` (vault root)\n- `conventions/` — the six rules,\n  writing style included\n- `templates/` — decided once, not every time\n- `claude_memory/` — behaviour, never facts\n- `log.md` — every input, one line\n- `my_tasks.md` — a query, stores nothing",
      "x": -620,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 350,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "archive",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 06_archive — RESTING\nFinished projects, old daily notes.\n\n**Never deleted.** The decisions outlive the project.",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "knowledge",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 04_knowledge — MEMORY\nThe permanent wiki. Where things **compound**.\n\n`it/` · `people/` · `company/` · `references/`",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 215,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# How this vault works\n\nEight folders. Material always flows **downward**.",
      "x": 0,
      "y": -520,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 120
    },
    {
      "id": "inbox",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 01_inbox — INPUT\nRaw material. A **buffer, never a storage**.\nThings may wait here.\nThey may not move in.",
      "x": 0,
      "y": -320,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 150,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "daily",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 05_daily_notes\nLOG — what happened, day by day.\n\nRuns **alongside** everything.\nWeekly reports are built from it.",
      "x": 770,
      "y": -120,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "private",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 07_private\nOutside the flow.\n\n**Not in git.** Fails closed:\nif unsure, it goes here.",
      "x": -520,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "note",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**The rule that makes it work:**\n\nNothing stays where it landed.\nEverything here is on its way\nsomewhere else.",
      "x": 720,
      "y": -375,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 130
    }
  ],
